725187f-a.title: Queens: 30th Street - 40th Avenue
725187f-a.text:
30th Street (left), at the N.E. corner of 40th Avenue,
looking northeastward toward the I.R.T. elevated on 31st
Street.
P. L. Sperr  September 5, 1940
NO REPRODUCTIONS

725323f-a.title: Queens: 40th Avenue - 30th Street
725323f-a.text:
Fortieth Ave. (formerly Payntor Ave., left foreground), at the
N.W. corner of 30th Street (formerly Lockwood Street). The two frame
structures at the left background, rear views, face on 29th Street,
formerly 122-124 Academy Street.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
